n class=\"s1\">disturbed by man</span></em></strong></p>', 'Environment and Man', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '77-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-01-15 05:48:13', '2018-01-15 05:48:13', '', 77, 'http://localhost/wpp3/77-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
